Name: Level Up Simulator
About the game: A vast majority of people love to trade trading cards, whether it is in real life or virtual cards, this makes level-up simulator perfect for you! Buy, sell, trade, and craft cards to level up, unlock more methods of trading to profit more, and level up further! Key features of the game: Level System Currency System Buy and Sell Trading Cards Buy and Sell Foil Trading Cards Card Bots Foil Card Bots Trash Bot Key Bot Stat Tracking Dynamic Pricing (Keep track of the market price, if not you may lose money) Steam Achievements Unfortunately, Steam trading cards cant be added right now, but they are made and ready to be added once I am allowed
